<D>__{somehow, in the middle of this ... carnival, kurtz had grown into something a gifted officer; a great man. somehow, he was the only light in this hopeless, hopeless darkness. and now i was too late he was probably gone, disappeared... by a grenade rolled into his tent or by some spear on the head. christ, i felt like howling like those animals in the fog.}
